-- Xinjiang Goldwind Science to Buy China Wind Companies From Golden Concord
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-23T22:53:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/xinjiang-goldwind-science-to-buy-china-wind-companies-from-golden-concord.html
Xinjiang Goldwind Science &
Technology Co. plans to pay as much as 200 million yuan for two
wind power equipment makers, according to a statement to
Shenzhen’s stock exchange.  Goldwind will buy an 85 percent stake in a wind power
equipment maker based in China’s Jiangsu province from Golden
Concord Holdings Ltd., according to the statement. Goldwind will
also buy a 25 percent stake in another wind power equipment
maker from Golden Concord that’s based in the Chinese province
of Inner Mongolia, it said. The equipment maker based in Jiangsu
owns the remaining 75 percent stake in the Inner Mongolia-based
company, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  